properties.headline: Gale Watch issued February 19 at 8:57PM CST until February 22 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...SOUTHWESTERLY GALES POSSIBLE FRIDAY AFTERNOON AND EVENING
FOR NORTHERN LAKE MICHIGAN...

* WHAT...Southwest winds to 30 kt with gusts up to 40 kt and
waves 7 to 10 feet possible.

* WHERE...Northern half of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From Friday afternoon through Friday evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and waves.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM FRIDAY AFTERNOON THROUGH FRIDAY EVENING
